---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Dynamic Computer Science professional with proven experience in solutions development, technical presentations, and project management. Adept at managing cross-functional stakeholder relationships and translating complex technical concepts for diverse audiences. Combines strong technical aptitude with business acumen to deliver innovative solutions that drive measurable outcomes.  
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bachelor of Applied Computer Science"
      subtitle="September 2021 to October 2024 at Dalhousie University, Halifax, NS"
    >
      GPA: 3.74; Received Morven Gentleman Prize, Sexton Scholar and Dean's List (Top 15%)
      Awarded 1st Place at Scotiabank's Canada's Top Students Product Challenge<br>
      Coursework: HTML, CSS, API Integration, Database Management, Software Development
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Solution Developer Intern"
      subtitle="January 2024 to May 2024 at Emera Inc., Halifax, NS"
    >
      • Developed custom HTML business analytics tool that improved operational visibility by 20%<br>
      • Collaborated with stakeholders to gather requirements and deliver technical presentations<br>
      • Authored comprehensive technical documentation (20+ pages) that reduced support inquiries by 40%<br>
      • Managed multiple concurrent projects while meeting all deadlines<br>
      • Fetched large datasets from third-party APIs and implemented data transformation processes<br>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Product Educator"
      subtitle="August 2024 to March 2025 at Lululemon, Halifax, NS"
    >
      • Served as trusted advisor to customers by effectively communicating technical specifications<br>
      • Collaborated with cross-functional teams to optimize product presentation and customer experience<br>
      • Increased conversion rates by 15% through data-driven analysis and strategic improvements<br>
      • Demonstrated adaptability in a fast-paced environment while maintaining exceptional client relationships<br>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Project Manager"
      subtitle="August 2022 to January 2023 at TEDxDalhousieU, Halifax, NS"
    >
      • Spearheaded event execution, managing a 15-member team and multiple complex projects<br>
      • Created and maintained project documentation using knowledge management platforms<br>
      • Designed promotional content using Canva and video processing tools<br>
      • Implemented process improvements for project tracking, increasing transparency by 30%<br>
      • Leveraged data analytics tools to track metrics, resulting in 35% increased attendance<br>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Marketing Analyst Intern"
      subtitle="May 2022 to September 2022 at CIBC, Toronto, ON"
    >
      • Applied business analytics to large datasets to translate complex data into actionable insights<br>
      • Developed comprehensive business reviews using Tableau for executive presentations<br>
      • Managed vendor relationships, demonstrating strong stakeholder management skills<br>
      • Created technical content and visual assets that drove 30% increase in engagement<br>
      • Collaborated with 10+ stakeholders across departments as primary point of contact<br>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Technical Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-6">
    <li>HTML</li>
    <li>CSS</li>
    <li>API Integration</li>
    <li>SQL</li>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>Java</li>
    <li>Tableau</li>
    <li>Google Analytics</li>
    <li>Confluence</li>
    <li>Microsoft Office Suite</li>
    <li>Google Workspace</li>
    <li>Jira</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Additional Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-2 columns-1 mx-6 mb-6">
    <li>Technical Presentations</li>
    <li>Requirements Gathering</li>
    <li>Cross-functional Team Collaboration</li>
    <li>Process Improvement</li>
    <li>Project Management</li>
    <li>Agile Scrum Methodology</li>
    <li>Technical Documentation</li>
    <li>Data Analysis</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Additional Information</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10">
    <li>Available for domestic travel within Canada & United States</li>
    <li>Learning technology enthusiast with interest in LMS industry</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
